videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum gets the block on North Carolina's Luke Maye on the fast break.
videos.headline: Jayson Tatum denies Luke Maye on the layup

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen makes two 3-pointers in the opening minutes against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen knocks down a pair of early 3-pointers

videos.description: Duke's Matt Jones finds Harry Giles under the basket for a layup to tie the game at 33-33.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to Giles lay-in

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen makes his fourth 3-pointer of the half to give Duke a 40-39 lead at halftime.
videos.headline: Allen hits a 3-pointer to end the half

videos.description: Jayson Tatum finds the open Grayson Allen and he hits his 3rd 3-pointer of the first half.
videos.headline: Allen gets the pass and drains the 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen makes 4-of-7 attempts from 3-point range in the first half against North Carolina. He's tied with a game-high 14 points at the break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Grayson Allen has big first half against UNC) 2017/02/09

videos.headline: Grayson Allen has big first half against UNC
Allen stays hot and hits his 5th 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen continues his hot shooting from beyond the arc, knocking down his sixth 3-pointer against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Allen makes his sixth 3-pointer of the game

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum throws down a monster dunk over North Carolina's Kennedy Meeks.
videos.headline: Tatum posterizes Meeks on a vicious dunk

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen slams home a two-handed dunk to put Duke up by 6.
videos.headline: Allen throws down a two-handed slam

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen and Luke Kennard talk about how it feels to win at home against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen and Luke Kennard on how it feels to beat North Carolina

videos.description: Grayson Allen scores a game-high 25 points while Jayson Tatum adds 19 points and nine rebounds in No. 18 Duke's 86-78 win over No. 8 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Duke tops UNC behind Allen's 25

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard joins Scott Van Pelt to describe the "unbelievable" environment at Cameron Indoor Stadium when facing North Carolina and how Jayson Tatum came through huge in the second half to get the victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Kennard on UNC rivalry and atmosphere) 2017/02/09 SVP SC ESHEET

videos.headline: Kennard on UNC rivalry and atmosphere
